text: Agricola Borcea is a Romanian football team from Borcea, Călărași County, which plays in Liga III since 2017. The club was founded in 1980 and also plays in the Romanian Cup after they beated CSM Slatina on penalties. ==History== Agricola Borcea was founded in 1980. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Romanian football clubs
